==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: gay-wings
<hw>gay-wings</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>A common trailing perennial
milkwort (<spn>Polygala paucifolia</spn>) of eastern North America
having leaves like wintergreen and usually rosy-purple flowers with
winged sepals.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> flowering wintergreen, gaywings, bird-on-the-wing,
fringed polygala, <spn>Polygala paucifolia</spn>.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

